Contribute Guide
Getting started (Local gitbook)

git clone https://github.com/techbootcamp/book.git
yarn global add gitbook-cli or npm install gitbook-cli -g
cd book
yarn or npm install
gitbook update
gitbook serve
go to localhost:4000

Some features you can include in this gitbook
Check the markdown of this page to see the source
Youtube videos

Mermaid Diagrams (helpful for flow or process diagrams)
See the Official Mermaid website on how to use this cool tool.
